import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Nav, Navbar } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import './NavigationBar.css'

export default class NavigationBar extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Navbar expand="lg">
        <Navbar.Brand href="/">Raising the Bar</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse>
          <Nav pullRight>
            <NavItem eventKey={1} componentClass={Link} to="/">
              Home
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem eventKey={2} componentClass={Link} to="/simulation">
              Simulation
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem eventKey={3} componentClass={Link} to="/creator">
              Creator
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem eventKey={4} componentClass={Link} to="/workshop">
              Workshop
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem eventKey={5} componentClass={Link} to="/recipe">
              Recipe
            </NavItem>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Navbar>
    )
  }
}
